{"tid":275700,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"《專訪太空艙主》原來係二房東　投資十萬望有錢賺","createTime":"2017-06-08T08:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T20:59:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"500fcc33153ce6da9d9449876869fb5b56bdfc85","tid":275700,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2016年10月26日<br />\n近日在租屋網Hit爆的西營盤「太空艙」分租床位，原來是該單位的二房東傑作。這名二房東，昨日就同《壹》仔分享他為何會有這個太空概念。<br />\n<br />\n這個位於西營盤德輔道西一唐樓的八百多呎單位，二房東王先生早前以月租二萬三千元租下來。王先生同《壹》仔講，由想找其他租客分擔租金，因此想到再分租。他看到日本及內地太空艙大行其道，又自覺香港有市場，於是投資了約十萬元設置太空艙租出去，「有錢賺當然好，回到本先。」<br />\n<br />\n單位內有三個不同大細的房間，客廳有四個太空艙，另其餘三房則分別放置兩個太空艙。王表示自己一家四口現居於上址，每人一艙，另外六個艙將會出租。他又強調，業主知道自己將單位改成太空艙。<br />\n<br />\n他又指現還未確實租金，但絕對會低於5100元，水電煤全包。王強調艙內「一應俱全」，電制Wifi均有提供，而且艙身防火，自住絕對安全。如果太空艙成搶手貨，王生更不排除將自己住緊的四個艙租埋出去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8z_S1yk5U9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8z_S1yk5U9Q&d=2hD%2FZEoAO43rLkHu5t1v6EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ce1f9f03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8z_S1yk5U9Q</a>"},{"pid":"db34d54541c49146f90db87edd8c967382a4524a","tid":275700,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qLgpZhrGXk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqLgpZhrGXk0&d=2hD%2FZEoAO43rLkHu5t1v6EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=dd582f32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qLgpZhrGXk0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港太空艙5000蚊一個　記者瞓身實測<br />\n<br />\n發佈日期：2016年11月20日<br />\n【本報訊】香港生活迫人，廁所樓上房怕有衞生問題，太空艙式籠屋床位「有冇得諗」？本報記者直擊位於太子舊樓太空艙單位，發現有人於一個約500方呎單位，踩界擺放8個太空艙出租，每個艙位月租4,000至4,300元，若全數出租，每月租金收入逾3.3萬元。有律師指，經營者可能已犯法。"},{"pid":"a1d353a179c11fc1e0803e792bf6b465706ef20d","tid":275700,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"「太空艙」真係住得過？ 記者實試月租＄5100 酒店式管理<br />\n發佈日期：2016年10月25日<br />\n酒店式管理：十天換一次床單、藍紫色燈光、拍卡出入、USB充電就在身旁、有電視、LED照明、兩米乘一米床褥、可調節冷氣系統！<br />\n實情係咪咁？睇片跟記者體驗下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3umNtjaXVNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3umNtjaXVNs&d=2hD%2FZEoAO43rLkHu5t1v6EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=631a459d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3umNtjaXVNs</a>"},{"pid":"e18b99f84aa7b9e016f0dac0fed8f3b3ea45ac98","tid":275700,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"就算業主知道左改左做tube<br />\n但張租約列明左唔可以再分租而且又冇改<br />\n隨時可以釘死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfbeffb82f309a764ac68cbece53f2aaa33ab62","tid":275700,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"$5100?<br />\n你自己會唔會入去住先"},{"pid":"7befc070176d86a83d7cce2e4b34d02ce7f923b4","tid":275700,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"十天換一次床單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86748447426630f100828456521aa13723159f14","tid":275700,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算業主知道左改左做tube<br />\n但張租約列明左唔可以再分租而且又冇改<br />\n隨時可以釘死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等緊睇佢賺唔賺到<br />\n一收到風賺到錢就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb36bf35b251fc724809399aecbd3d9725565397","tid":275700,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"